          "content": "## SWOT Analysis\nSWOT analyzes Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, and Threats.\n\n### Internal Factors\n- Strengths\n- Weaknesses\n\n### External Factors\n- Opportunities\n- Threats\n\n### Importance\nHelps strategic decision-making.",
