          "content": "## Porter's Five Forces\nFramework to analyze industry competition.\n\n### Forces\n- Threat of new entrants\n- Bargaining power of buyers\n- Bargaining power of suppliers\n- Threat of substitutes\n- Competitive rivalry\n\n### Importance\nHelps determine industry profitability.",
          "examples": ["Tech industry competition", "Retail rivalry"],
          "common_mistakes": [
            "Ignoring substitutes",
            "Underestimating competition"
          ],
          "qna": [
            {
              "q": "What is Porter’s model?",
              "a": "Industry analysis framework."
            },
            { "q": "How many forces?", "a": "Five." },
            { "q": "Why important?", "a": "Assess competition." },
            { "q": "Example?", "a": "Market rivalry." },
            { "q": "Risk?", "a": "Ignoring substitutes." }
          ]
        },
